FBIS3-929 "drafr051_c_94008" FBIS-AFR-94-051 Document Type:Daily Report 15 Mar 1994 REPUBLIC OF SOUTH AFRICA Afrikaner Radio on Destabilization of KwaZulu MB1603110894 Pretoria Radio Pretoria in Afrikaans 1700 GMT 15 Mar 94 MB1603110894 Pretoria Radio Pretoria Language: Afrikaans Article Type:BFN [Text] The first steps to destabilize kwaZulu have already taken place. The situation in Umlazi is extremely tense due to strikes in the area. Announcements on SABC [South African Broadcasting Corporation] news services that several members of the IFP [Inkatha Freedom Party] have joined other parties since they want to take part in the election, could very well be a ploy to sow confusion in IFP ranks.
